{"id":"ab8e1c45-c6d4-47be-a8d4-3ac9fec85162","name":"The Whale's Bane: Phaedra Douglas","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 120, 0)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(47, 76, 188); color: inherit\">\"I’m going to turn you into a bloody pulp.”</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Any sea monster hunter worth their salt knows the name Phaedra Douglas and the many titles that cling to it like barnacles.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>“The Douglas Family’s Greatest Prodigy”</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>“Captain of The Hope’s Star”</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>“The Strongest Sea Monster Hunter”</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>“The Sea Monster in Human Skin”</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>All these titles do describe parts of her, but the title that rings the truest is:</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>“The Mad Hunter”</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Because underneath all those titles, the true essence of Phaedra Douglas is and  always has been...</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>A madwoman who is obsessed with killing a whale</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 120, 0)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(47, 76, 188); color: inherit\">Clear Obsession:</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/image/-Cl6D04gaV9EZfGMhK-hy.webp\"></em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 120, 0)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(47, 76, 188); color: inherit\">\"Another hunt begins!\"</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=